channel.title: Teleother Help
channel.description:
Hey.
Well, on my server, when someone clicks the teleother spell, then clicks another person, the interface comes up.
The Falador interface one for teleother falador, where it says "w/e wishes to teleport you to falador!"
and you can click accept or decline.
and the Camelot, and Lumbridge ones.
Yeah, well, the interfaces come up when a person uses one of the spels on someone. BUT It won't let you accept or decline the interface..
You click decline, nothing happens. You click accept, nothing happens.
I want to know how to make it tele you to falador, for the falador one, camelot for the camelot one, and lumbridge for the other one, when you click the accept button.
Please help a.s.a.p.
Jube.
